---
import { Picture } from "astro:assets";

import { APP_NAME } from "../common";
import TopImage from "../images/top.png";
import AddDialogImage from "../images/add-dialog.png";
import DetailImage from "../images/detail.png";
---

<div class="flex flex-col gap-3">
  <div class="flex flex-row gap-5 max-w-1/2">
    <Picture src={TopImage} alt="Top" />
    <Picture src={AddDialogImage} alt="Add Dialog" />
    <Picture src={DetailImage} alt="Detail" />
  </div>

  <div>
    <p>
      {APP_NAME} is a desktop app that makes it easy to log your daily activities.
    </p>
    <p>
      Just enter the date, activity, and any notes, and youâ€™ll quickly capture
      what you did that day.
    </p>
    <p>
      This app is useful in a wide range of situations, from keeping track of
      daily moments to recording progress at work.
    </p>
  </div>

  <div>
    Use Cases:

    <ul class="list-disc list-inside">
      <li>
        Personal Notes: Remember where you went with friends or how you spent
        your free time, perfect for tracking personal memories.
      </li>

      <li>
        Work Activity Log: Record daily tasks and work progress to review later.
      </li>
    </ul>
  </div>

  <div>
    <p>
      With its simple interface, Activity Pulse Logger supports you in keeping a
      clear record of your activities.
    </p>
  </div>
</div>
